</td>
<td style="width: 91.74%; background: transparent; padding: 0cm;" width="91%">
<p style="margin-top:6.0pt"><span lang="VI" style="font-size:
  10.0pt">(3.2) <i>X</i> = </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt">invSubCells<i>(X)</i></span></p>
</td>
