  10.0pt">(3)</span></p>
</td>
<td style="width: 91.74%; background: transparent; padding: 0cm;" valign="bottom" width="91%">
<p style="margin-top:6.0pt"><i><span style="font-size:10.0pt">C</span></i><i><span lang="VI" style="font-size:10.0pt"> =</span></i><i><span style="font-size:10.0pt">
  X </span></i><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><img height="16" src="//files.thuvienphapluat.vn/doc2htm/00921576_files/image016.jpg" width="14"><i>&nbsp;K<sub>post</sub></i></span></p>
</td>
